('FLReq-996803', '播放音乐的视频从USB媒体 Play music of video from USB Media', 'Play music of video from USB Media
Preconditions:
The IVI system is powered on and connected to the internet. The IVI system supports playback from USB device. The user has accessed the media interface on the IVI system. Main Scenario:
The user initiates the IVI system and navigates to the media interface. The IVI system displays options for various media sources, including USB device. The user selects the "USB" option within the media interface. The IVI system accesses the USB device and displays available media files. The user chooses a preferred media file The IVI system open file and starts streaming the content through the vehicle''s audio system and in case of video picture to the stream to the screen The user enjoys the content from the chosen file Post-condition:
The user successfully operates and listens and (or) watches to the selected media file via the IVI system. The user can get additional media information like Artist, Album, Album Art.



