('FLReq-1020702', '改变仪表板上的个人UI模式 Changing Personal UI Mode on the Instrument Panel​​​', 'Changing Personal UI Mode on the Instrument Panel
Preconditions:


The vehicle''s Instrument Panel is powered on and operational. The Instrument Panel is equipped with a user interface that supports changing UI themes or color schemes. The system is capable of offering pre-defined UI themes or color schemes. 

Main Scenario:


The user accesses the settings or personalization menu on the Instrument Panel. The UI customization options are displayed, presenting several pre-defined UI themes or color schemes. The user reviews the available themes or color schemes, each corresponding to different moods or preferences (e.g., "Relaxing Blue," "Energetic Red," "Professional Black," etc.). The user selects a preferred theme or color scheme from the available choices. The Instrument Panel updates its UI according to the user''s selection, displaying the chosen theme or color scheme. 

Alternative Scenario: Mood Detection for Automatic Theme Selection


The user navigates to the mood detection feature within the settings menu on the Instrument Panel. The system prompts the user to activate the mood detection feature. The system utilizes available data sources, such as biometric sensors or other mood-detecting technologies, to identify the user''s mood. Based on the detected mood, the system automatically selects an appropriate theme or color scheme for the UI. The Instrument Panel updates its UI to reflect the automatically chosen theme or color scheme corresponding to the detected mood. 

Post-condition:


In the main scenario, the user successfully changes the UI mode on the Instrument Panel to a selected theme or color scheme, offering user-driven personalization. In the alternative scenario, the system adapts the UI based on detected mood, providing a personalized interface without direct user input. The selected or automatically chosen UI theme remains active until the user decides to change it manually or the system detects a different mood triggering an automatic theme change. 

改变仪表板上的个人UI模式
先决条件:

车辆的仪表盘通电并可操作。
仪表板配备了一个用户界面，支持更改UI主题或配色方案。
该系统能够提供预定义的UI主题或配色方案。

