Human: Fleet owner/manager/operator, Carsharing Driver
System: Atom telematics system


Preconditions:
The connection parameters are configured. The list and rules for receiving telemetry data are configured. Triggers: Atom vehicle''s systems turns on.


Main Scenario:
Atom telematics system collects and aggregates the data from systems, sensors in accordance with the established set or Regular Data Set. Atom telematics system sends the collected and aggregated data to Fleet owner/manager/operator a given frequency. Fleet owner/manager/operator regularly receives a complete set of data and analyzes it via out_82 third party FMS. Alternative Scenario:
2a. If the vehicle is outside the network coverage area, the data is saved to the on-board storage medium.
3a. When the vehicle is within the network coverage the Atom telematics system sends the data from the on-board carrier to Fleet owner/manager/operator.


