('I-33560', 'Notify Passenger about the driver-only VA command', 'Use Case Name: Notify Passenger about the driver-only VA command
Goal: Block passengers from issuing driver-only VA commands.
Scope: Add functions to detect who issues the commands and restricts command execution based on the detected role.
Context: There are voice commands which might affect the driving process, and it''s necessary to restrict the command execution based on the different conditions, i.e. person identification, driving cycle.
